ActAn Act to amend certain Acts and to make certain consequential amendments (firearms)
SubjectOrder Fixing March 7, 2025 as the Day on Which Section 34 and Subsections 35(2) and 38(1) of An Act to amend certain Acts and to make certain consequential amendments (firearms) Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing March 7, 2025 as the day on which section 34 and subsections 35(2) and 38(1) of AN ACT TO AMEND CERTAIN ACTS AND TO MAKE CERTAIN CONSEQUENTIAL AMENDMENTS (FIREARMS) COME INTO FORCE in order to enable licence suspension amendments in the Firearms Act.
AttachmentsAttachment
